class="entry-subtitle">An overlooked ruling could force small businesses to pay sales tax in dozens, even hundreds, of jurisdictions where they have no representation.</h2><p class="meta"> <span class="byline author vcard"> <a href="https://reason.com/people/eric-boehm/" title="Posts by Eric Boehm" class="author url fn" rel="author">Eric Boehm</a> </span> <span class="pipe">|</span> <time class="updated" datetime="2019-03-19T10:00:00-04:00">3.19.2019 10:00 AM</time></p><div class="rcom-social-tools"><a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2019%2F03%2F19%2Fthe-supreme-courts-online-sales-tax-ruli%2F" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--facebook" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Facebook" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2019%2F03%2F19%2Fthe-supreme-courts-online-sales-tax-ruli%2F&text=Which+states+charge+sales+taxes+for+fireproof+underwear%3F+Thanks+to+the+Supreme+Court%2C+this+small+business+owner+has+to+know.+&via=reason" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--twitter" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Twitter" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a><a href="https://www.reddit.com/submit?url=https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2F2019%2F03%2F19%2Fthe-supreme-courts-online-sales-tax-ruli%2F&title=Which+states+charge+sales+taxes+for+fireproof+underwear%3F+Thanks+to+the+Supreme+Court%2C+this+small+business+owner+has+to+know.+" target="_blank" class="rcom-social-tools--button rcom-social--reddit" data-ga-click="true" data-ga-category="Social Share Button Clicked" data-ga-action="Social Share Click - Reddit" data-ga-label="article header"><i class="fab fa-reddit"></i></a><a href="mailto:?subject=Shared+From+Reason.com%3A+Wh